https://leetcode.com/problems/counting-bits/description/

1 2ms 100%  !!!!!!!!
  高位的1其实就是2的n次方，就是flag的值
  class Solution {
    public int[] countBits(int num) {
        int[] ans = new int[num+1];
        ans[0] = 0;
        if(num > 0)
            ans[1] = 1;
        int flag = 1;
        for(int i=2;i<=num;i++){
            if(i%flag == 0) flag *= 2;
            ans[i] = 1+ ans[i-flag];
        }
        return ans;
    }
}
感觉我很强，discuss里面都是用&的瓜皮，规律都不会找
